title: [Gyldemar Forest, Overgrown Path]
description: A fallen tree and a mass of low-hanging vines nearly block the path.  The thick growth prevents any breeze from reaching the path.  Nearby, a woodpecker works hard on another tree.
A fallen tree and a mass of low-hanging vines nearly block the path.  The thick growth prevents any breeze from reaching the path.  Nearby, an owl hoots softly, passing the night with his song.
